cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/164576/', '', 'Butabarbital, Thiopental, Butalbital, Methylphenobarbital, Ethchlorvynol, Dichloralphenazone, Ephedrine, Tropicamide, Phenylephrine, Rolapitant, Aprepitant', '', 1767369485);
